 a rigorous maintenance and upgrade program to keep our fleet in line with the regulations and operating standards of the regions in which we operate in addition our teams of certified mechanics crane inspectors and port engineers continuously monitor the status of our fleet to ensure a standard of operational reliability   for more information please contact our international liftboat sales team   gemfish     current region west africa   leg length  ft   max water depth  ft   crane capacity  st   total berths marine crew   pob pob   deck area  sq ft   max deck load  mt    technical specifications  tapertail     current region west africa   leg length  ft   max water depth  ft   crane capacity  st   total berths marine crew   pob pob   deck area  sq ft   max deck load  mt    technical specifications  solefish     current region west africa   leg length  ft   max water depth  ft   crane capacity  st   total berths marine crew   pob pob   deck area  sq ft   max deck load  mt    technical specifications  triggerfish     current region west africa   leg length  ft   max water depth  ft   crane capacity  st   total berths marine crew   pob pob   deck area  sq ft   max deck load  mt    technical specifications  scamp     current region west africa   leg length  ft   max water depth  ft   crane capacity  st   total berths marine crew   pob pob   deck area  sq ft   max deck load  mt    technical specifications  rudderfish     current region west africa   leg length  ft   max water depth  ft   crane capacity  st   total berths marine crew   pob pob   deck area  sq ft   max deck load  mt    technical specifications  pilot fish     current region west africa   leg length  ft   max water depth  ft   crane capacity  st   total berths marine crew   pob pob   deck area  sq ft   max deck load  mt    technical specifications  bluefish     current region west africa   leg length  ft   max water depth  ft   crane capacity  st   total berths marine crew   pob pob   deck area  sq ft   m